      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Full-length shot of two men seated on chairs and of a boy standing behind them. One of the men is wearing town attire and holding a 'šubara' (a man's winter fur hat worn as part of folk attire) in his hands. The other one is dressed in traditional, oriental-style clothes, holding a 'fez' (felt hat). The boy is dressed in a school/cadet uniform. He is also holding a cap.</ab>
